61
00:02:43,157 --> 00:02:45,193
Merry Christmas, Daddy.

62
00:02:45,260 --> 00:02:47,862
It's not Christmas yet, baby.

63
00:02:47,930 --> 00:02:50,632
Haven't you been keeping
your advent calendar?

64
00:02:50,700 --> 00:02:52,701
