I kill first.

110
00:04:32,384 --> 00:04:33,917
No, please. Stop.

111
00:04:33,985 --> 00:04:35,119
Y-You don't have to do this.

112
00:04:35,187 --> 00:04:36,320
You know what?

113
00:04:39,024 --> 00:04:40,057
I'm not feeling

114
00:04:40,125 --> 00:04:41,993
